Hey there, sunshine

That's often how I'm greeted - fitting for a blonde obsessed with the color yellow. Anyways, this always-smiling ray of sun designed and developed an ode to oddities that happen when architecture, computer science, animation, hand craft, and digital precision merge to shed light on a little bit of quirkiness.
